# FastAPI View Objects

<p align="center">
    <em>FastAPI-VO, view objects for FastAPI designed for simplicity.</em>
</p>

<p align="center">
  <a href="https://github.com/rennancockles/fastapi-vo/actions?query=workflow%3ALint%20and%20Test" target="_blank">
